# Copy this file to .env.local for local development.
# On Vercel/Netlify, set this in the project's environment variables instead.
#
# Get a free key at https://aistudio.google.com -> Get API key -> Create API key
#
# NOTE: because this is a client-only app with no backend, this key ships
# inside the browser bundle and is visible to anyone who opens devtools.
# Google's own docs recommend a backend proxy for production use, which
# this app does not have. Don't reuse this key anywhere sensitive — free
# tier rate limits bound the worst case, but this is not a secure way to
# hold a real secret long-term.
VITE_GOOGLE_API_KEY=your_key_here
